00:34:47,385 --> 00:34:48,186
That was amazing.

590
00:34:58,930 --> 00:34:59,797
Chenchen, call Ye Sisi in.

591
00:35:02,133 --> 00:35:02,667
Me?

592
00:35:03,267 --> 00:35:03,568
Okay.

593
00:35:03,968 --> 00:35:04,335
Wait.

594
00:35:06,037 --> 00:35:06,571
Have her scrub in.

595
00:35:07,238 --> 00:35:07,638
Copy.

596
00:35:14,846 --> 00:35:15,213
Hello?

597
00:35:17,615 --> 00:35:17,949
Okay.

598
00:35:19,984 --> 00:35:20,384
Director.

599
00:35:21,119 --> 00:35:21,486
Go ahead.

600
00:35:24,489 --> 00:35:25,022
I'll be right there.

601
00:35:39,971 --> 00:35:40,605
May you live a long life.

602
00:36:02,426 --> 00:36:02,994
Director Lin.

603
00:36:03,995 --> 00:36:05,029
You finish closing this case.

604
00:36:08,633 --> 00:36:09,567
Every life we save is one life gained.

605
00:36:27,084 --> 00:36:27,652
Liu Dong, Xiao Zhu.

606
00:36:29,086 --> 00:36:30,054
If she makes a mistake,

607
00:36:30,488 --> 00:36:31,355
I'll hold both of you responsible.

608
00:36:35,226 --> 00:36:35,693
Uh...

609
00:36:37,962 --> 00:36:38,930
All right. Just focus on doing it.

610
00:36:39,030 --> 00:36:39,764
If the sky falls,

611
00:36:40,464 --> 00:36:41,799
he and I will hold it up.

612
00:36:43,868 --> 00:36:44,969
Trust yourself. Go on.

613
00:37:52,637 --> 00:37:52,970
Director.

614
00:37:55,206 --> 00:37:56,374
The closure was pretty good.

615
00:38:02,113 --> 00:38:02,747
Let me introduce everyone.

616
00:38:03,314 --> 00:38:04,081
This is

617
00:38:04,749 --> 00:38:05,950
Director Ji,

618
00:38:06,317 --> 00:38:06,851
whom Dr. Fang invited.

619
00:38:06,951 --> 00:38:07,785
She's from

620
00:38:07,785 --> 00:38:08,252
our hospital's ICU.

621
00:38:08,486 --> 00:38:09,353
An old comrade-in-arms of mine,

622
00:38:09,787 --> 00:38:11,255
and a top ICU specialist.

623
00:38:11,722 --> 00:38:12,690
You're exaggerating, Head Nurse.

624
00:38:12,990 --> 00:38:14,125
This is our lead surgeon,

625
00:38:14,225 --> 00:38:14,725
Director Lin.

626
00:38:15,159 --> 00:38:16,827
And this is Director Zhou.

627
00:38:17,128 --> 00:38:18,362
Director Lin, I've heard so much about you.

628
00:38:19,764 --> 00:38:21,465
We'll be relying on everyone from here on.

629
00:38:21,599 --> 00:38:22,400
Let's work together

630
00:38:22,533 --> 00:38:23,267
to protect this patient.

631
00:38:24,368 --> 00:38:25,569
Thank you for overseeing things, Director Ji.

632
00:38:26,370 --> 00:38:28,005
Postoperative care after artificial heart implantation

633
00:38:28,172 --> 00:38:28,906
is full of risks.

634
00:38:29,707 --> 00:38:30,875
Respiratory and circulatory status,

635
00:38:31,309 --> 00:38:31,976
the nervous system,

636
00:38:32,076 --> 00:38:33,044
cardiac and renal function—

637
00:38:33,144 --> 00:38:34,045
all require close monitoring.

638
00:38:34,311 --> 00:38:35,646
This is Dongli's first such case.

639
00:38:36,013 --> 00:38:36,547
With you here,

640
00:38:36,814 --> 00:38:37,648
I feel much more reassured.

641
00:38:38,683 --> 00:38:39,383
We still have many hurdles

642
00:38:39,517 --> 00:38:41,118
to get through over the next two days.

643
00:38:42,353 --> 00:38:43,487
Set up a rotating duty roster.

644
00:38:43,654 --> 00:38:45,156
Someone must remain at the bedside every second.

645
00:38:45,456 --> 00:38:45,790
Understood.

646
00:38:46,023 --> 00:38:46,724
For these forty-eight hours,

647
00:38:46,791 --> 00:38:48,326
the head nurse and I will stay here.

648
00:38:48,592 --> 00:38:50,194
Engineer Xiao

649
00:38:50,494 --> 00:38:51,162
will stay with us as well.

650
00:38:51,429 --> 00:38:52,730
Keep the cardiac output from getting too high.

651
00:38:53,030 --> 00:38:53,864
Protect right ventricular function.

652
00:38:54,398 --> 00:38:54,932
Okay, Director Lin.

653
00:38:54,999 --> 00:38:55,533
I'm watching it.

654
00:38:56,233 --> 00:38:57,335
Circulation and heart rate

655
00:38:57,401 --> 00:38:58,069
are currently stable.

656
00:39:02,373 --> 00:39:02,840
Sister Beibei,

657
00:39:03,307 --> 00:39:04,775
central venous pressure should be kept

658
00:39:04,842 --> 00:39:05,943
between six and twelve millimeters of mercury.

659
00:39:06,243 --> 00:39:06,477
Okay.

660
00:39:06,510 --> 00:39:07,511
I ran into Director Sheng

661
00:39:07,511 --> 00:39:08,646
in the corridor.

662
00:39:10,481 --> 00:39:11,115
How did he react?

663
00:39:13,384 --> 00:39:13,951
I don't know.

664
00:39:15,052 --> 00:39:15,853
I didn't dare look at him.

665
00:39:20,424 --> 00:39:21,325
As for Director Sheng,

666
00:39:21,792 --> 00:39:22,526
don't put yourself forward.

667
00:39:23,194 --> 00:39:24,028
I'll take responsibility.

668
00:39:25,663 --> 00:39:26,664
I made the incision.

669
00:39:26,964 --> 00:39:27,932
What responsibility are you taking?

670
00:39:33,037 --> 00:39:34,205
At least we saved the patient.

671
00:39:38,843 --> 00:39:39,810
As for everything else,

672
00:39:39,810 --> 00:39:40,711
we'll have to take it one step at a time.

673
00:39:57,394 --> 00:39:57,795
Hang in there.

674
00:39:58,763 --> 00:39:59,663
Your promise to meet again

675
00:39:59,764 --> 00:40:00,631
and your birthday gifts

676
00:40:01,165 --> 00:40:02,066
are all waiting for you.

677
00:40:05,836 --> 00:40:06,403
Dr. Fang,

678
00:40:07,304 --> 00:40:08,272
does every bedside

679
00:40:08,773 --> 00:40:09,874
in your ICU

680
00:40:10,040 --> 00:40:10,875
have one of these?

681
00:40:12,243 --> 00:40:12,643
Yes.

682
00:40:13,811 --> 00:40:14,278
Not bad.

683
00:40:39,804 --> 00:40:40,571
Not bad.

684
00:40:40,805 --> 00:40:41,672
Will you let me operate on Du Yan?

685
00:40:42,072 --> 00:40:42,807
The surgery is imminent.

686
00:40:43,073 --> 00:40:44,074
I still think

687
00:40:44,442 --> 00:40:45,276
we need another discussion

688
00:40:45,376 --> 00:40:46,811
about the artificial heart device.

689
00:41:13,671 --> 00:41:15,506
Pick up, my dear auntie.

690
00:41:24,048 --> 00:41:24,682
Smells great.

691
00:41:29,386 --> 00:41:30,521
I checked your WeChat step count.

692
00:41:30,855 --> 00:41:31,922
You've done over twelve thousand steps.

693
00:41:32,756 --> 00:41:33,424
That many?

694
00:41:34,024 --> 00:41:34,592
No wonder

695
00:41:34,992 --> 00:41:36,126
I can barely feel

696
00:41:36,193 --> 00:41:37,294
either of my feet.

697
00:41:37,928 --> 00:41:38,529
You've worked hard.

698
00:41:39,129 --> 00:41:39,763
Thanks to you.

699
00:41:40,030 --> 00:41:41,632
Otherwise, we couldn't have completed

700
00:41:42,032 --> 00:41:42,867
It wasn't too bad.

701
00:41:43,234 --> 00:41:44,034
Luckily, everything turned out fine.

702
00:41:45,269 --> 00:41:46,070
Director Lin—

703
00:41:46,437 --> 00:41:47,505
what made him change his mind

704
00:41:47,605 --> 00:41:48,606
and agree to do the surgery?

705
00:41:50,307 --> 00:41:51,041
I don't know either.

706
00:41:52,276 --> 00:41:53,410
But I hope this time

707
00:41:53,811 --> 00:41:54,812
he has truly moved on.

708
00:41:58,549 --> 00:41:59,683
I'm actually more worried about you.

709
00:42:00,985 --> 00:42:02,152
Director Sheng definitely

710
00:42:02,186 --> 00:42:03,053
won't let this go.

711
00:42:03,687 --> 00:42:05,456
And you're caught between Qin Xiong and him.

712
00:42:06,490 --> 00:42:07,124
That'll make things even harder.

713
00:42:08,926 --> 00:42:09,627
It won't be hard.

714
00:42:09,994 --> 00:42:10,794
Both products

715
00:42:10,794 --> 00:42:11,795
are distributed by our company.

716
00:42:11,896 --> 00:42:12,830
At most,

717
00:42:12,930 --> 00:42:13,964
there's only a difference in profit margin.

718
00:42:14,331 --> 00:42:14,865
Mr. Qin won't

719
00:42:14,932 --> 00:42:15,799
do anything to me.

720
00:42:17,201 --> 00:42:17,601
Eat.

721
00:42:18,402 --> 00:42:19,069
You've been running around all day.

722
00:42:19,169 --> 00:42:20,037
I really am a little hungry.

723
00:42:52,069 --> 00:42:52,603
These goji berries—

724
00:42:52,603 --> 00:42:53,871
I brewed them especially for you.
